%html
  %head
    =csrf_meta_tag
    %title= page_title
    = stylesheet_link_tag 'application'
    = javascript_include_tag 'application'
  %body
    .splash-image
      %nav.logo.row
        .large-12.columns
          %a{href: "/", title: "winzo"}
            %span winzo
            / img src="img/logo.png" alt="winzo logo" /
      .row
        .large-12.small-12.columns.hero-copy
          %h1 Buy, sell and trade with friends
    .row
      .large-6.small-12.small-centered.columns.signup
        %a.button.large.radius{href: "#{signup_path}"} Sign Up Now
        .login
          %a{href: "#{login_path}"} or login here
    .section-green
      .row
        .large-6.small-12.columns
          %h2
            %strong Sellers:
            make new friends and clients, not just fans
          %ul
            %li Selling a product is as easy as updating your status with a photo, a description and a price.
            %li Your friends will be notified and can buy with one click.
            %li Keep being active on social media, knowing you'll gain clients, not just fans.
            %li Your friends will advertise your product on their feeds and bring more clients.
        .large-6.small-12.columns
          %h2
            %strong Buyers:
            discover new products and trusted sellers
          %ul
            %li See a list of your friends' recent purchases and discover new products you'll love.
            %li One-click hassle-free buying directly on winzo.
            %li If you're a seller too, you can trade your products for others.
            %li Sellers are verified by winzo before buying, so you can always trust your purchase.
